### 1. Login as admin and get JWT token
POST http://localhost:3000/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "admin@example.com",
    "password": "password123"
}

### 2. Update email (requires admin token)
PUT http://localhost:3000/update-email
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <INSERT-ADMIN-TOKEN-HERE>

{
    "newEmail": "new_admin@example.com"
}

### 3. Delete account (requires user token)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/delete-account
Authorization: Bearer <INSERT-USER-TOKEN-HERE>

### 4. Update role (requires admin token)
PUT http://localhost:3000/update-role
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <INSERT-ADMIN-TOKEN-HERE>

{
    "id": 2,
    "newRole": "admin"
}

### 5. Refresh token
POST http://localhost:3000/refresh-token
Authorization: Bearer <INSERT-OLD-TOKEN-HERE>
